# Reduce Cursor indexing noise; keep Second-Brain orchestration paths readable.
#
# .technical/** is NOT ignored: agents need prompt queues (legacy + parallel tracks),
# task-handoff-comms, tmp-prompt, eat-queue plans, Run-Telemetry, Validator/IRA outputs, etc.

# All JSONL elsewhere stay ignored; under .technical they are allowed (queue + audit + comms).
*.jsonl
!.technical/
!.technical/**

3-Resources/Watcher-*.md
!3-Resources/Watcher-Result.md
!3-Resources/Watcher-Result-sandbox.md
!3-Resources/Watcher-Result-godot.md

*.log

# Root-level technical files (must stay at root; Syncthing/Cursor read them here)
.stignore
